== 玩法  ==
在《守望先锋》中，黑影被归类为突击型英雄。她装备了低伤害、大容量的全自动衝鋒槍，用于近距离战斗。她可以入侵敌人与炮台，被入侵后，敌人将不能使用特殊或最终能力，但主要攻击方式仍可用。黑影的黑客技能也可以获取对手的生命值和最终能力状态，只要他们被侵入一分钟内仍在对手的视线中<ref name="creation"/>。黑影也可以扔出一个传动信标，使其短暂隐形并以爆发速度传送<ref name="creation"/>。她的终极能力是[[电磁脉冲|EMP]]爆炸，摧毁敌方屏障以及护盾，并且侵入范围内的所有敌人<ref name="gamespot sombra announced">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/overwatchs-next-character-sombra-officially-reveal/1100-6445128/|title=Overwatch's Next Character, Sombra, Officially Revealed|accessdate=2016-11-04|date=2016-11-04|last=Pereira|first=Chris|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-date=2016-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107181540/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/overwatchs-next-character-sombra-officially-reveal/1100-6445128/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 虚构生平 ==
黑影（“{{Lang|en|Sombra}}”的[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]意为「影子」）是[[鬥陣特攻角色列表|死神]]的联络人<ref name=":6" /><ref name="Kotaku ReaperSkull">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/overwatch-fans-sombra-investigation-reaps-a-skull-code-1785204389|title=''Overwatch'' Fans' Sombra Investigation Reaps A Skull Code|accessdate=2016-09-23|date=2016-08-12|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|last1=D'Anastasio|first1=Cecilia|archive-date=2016-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928113251/http://kotaku.com/overwatch-fans-sombra-investigation-reaps-a-skull-code-1785204389|dead-url=no}}</ref>，后者在“老兵”漫画<ref>{{Cite comic|writer=[[Michael_Chu|Michael Chu]]|artist=Bengal|story=Old Soldiers|title=Overwatch|issue=8|date=2016-07-21|publisher=[[暴雪娛樂|Blizzard Entertainment]]|page=2|panel=3|url=http://comic.playoverwatch.com/issues/overwatch/8/en-us/pdf/comic-overwatch-ana-2.pdf|format=PDF}} {{Wayback|url=http://comic.playoverwatch.com/issues/overwatch/8/en-us/pdf/comic-overwatch-ana-2.pdf |date=20161025181948 }}</ref>和游戏中的一些对话中提到过她<ref name=":2" /><ref name="ForbesMay">{{cite web|last1=Tassi|first1=Paul|title='Overwatch' Might Be Adding A Surprise 22nd Hero For Launch|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2016/05/20/overwatch-might-be-adding-a-surprise-22nd-hero-for-launch/#fa544a910f34|publisher=''[[福布斯|Forbes]]''|accessdate=2016-09-24|date=2016-05-20|archive-date=2016-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002125218/http://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2016/05/20/overwatch-might-be-adding-a-surprise-22nd-hero-for-launch/#fa544a910f34|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的[[母语|母语]]为西班牙语<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/8/24/12623736/overwatch-sombra-arg-clues-skycoder|title=Overwatch's Sombra mystery appears to be coming to a close|date=2016-08-24|last=Frank|first=Allegra|publisher=''[[Polygon|Polygon]]''|website=|access-date=2016-10-19|archive-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018164609/http://www.polygon.com/2016/8/24/12623736/overwatch-sombra-arg-clues-skycoder|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

有媒体推测她是一个墨西哥裔的黑客<ref name=":5" /><ref name=":6" />。她与[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]一个虚构的城镇多拉多有关，这一地图存在许多关于她的线索<ref name="Kotaku ReaperSkull" />，而且据推测她在多拉多活动<ref name=":6" /><ref name="TechNews AllWeKnow">{{cite web|url=http://www.technewstoday.com/31129-overwatch-all-we-know-about-the-sombra-arg/|title=Overwatch: All We Know About the Sombra ARG|accessdate=2016-09-23|date=2016-08-23|publisher=[[Tech_News_Today|Tech News Today]]|last1=Qureshi|first1=Badar|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916010815/http://www.technewstoday.com/31129-overwatch-all-we-know-about-the-sombra-arg/|archivedate=2016-09-16}}</ref>。

一个据称从内部暴雪开发者网站泄漏的消息称在智械危机期间，黑影“失去了一切”，在那场危机中{{Lang|en|Omnic}}机器人试图毁灭人类。泄漏的消息也称她在墨西哥与虚构的骷髅帮合作并最终被黑爪招募，后者是一个反派组织，死神也在其中<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" />。

